---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageSection from "../components/PageSection.astro";
import ContentSection from "../components/ContentSection.astro";
---
<Layout title="Photography | Techit Thawiang" navTitle="Photography<br/>captures life’s vivid harmony.">
    <PageSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p style="font-size:13px;">Warning: Massive image sizes.</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p class="big-paragraph">I started <span class="text-highlight">photographing</span> things when I was just 9 years old, thanks to my first smartphone. It was super cheap and not the best in quality, but it held a special place in my heart because my mum bought it for me.</p>
            <p class="big-paragraph">In 2023, I had the amazing opportunity to play with one of my friend's DSLR cameras. That day, I learned how to use a DSLR, and the difference in quality was astonishing compared to my early smartphone photos! It was a fun and eye-opening experience that reignited my passion for photography, making me excited to capture the world with better tools.</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p class="big-paragraph">Here's some of them.</p>
            <div class="grid is-col-min-10 is-gap-1 photography-grid">
                <a class="cell" href="https://j1.techit.win/images/photography/IMG_4183.JPG">
